methods.release:
Release ownership of this ReleasableLivenessManager, allowing any retained LivenessReferents to
 cleanup if they no longer have outstanding references.
methods.tryManage:
Attempt to add the specified referent to this manager.

:param referent: (io.deephaven.engine.liveness.LivenessReferent) - The referent to add
:return: (boolean) Whether the referent was in fact added

text: ReleasableLivenessManager to manage exactly one object, passed at construction time or managed later.
